  "gwSpecs": {
    "description": "Washbot LED CYMK 300 is a new versatile LED fixture that is designed to deliver a smooth, beautifully mixed color wash effect for large to small applications. Equipped with a 300W LED engine that can produce a bright and even projection, the Washbot’s impressive7- 31 degrees zoom range gives you the versatility to be utilized in multiple settings. With a smooth CYMK color mixing, it allows for multiple color combinations. The Kelvin color wheel allows for white color temperature adjustment from 6044K to 4159K. An additional color wheel with7 fixed colors is also included for fast color scrolling. It also offers a unique set of added colors that reside on the back end of the CYMK color wheels. With the ability to generate a multitude of color sequences the Washbot also features a prism that gives you the freedom to project unique effects onto any stage.",
